It isn't hard to not be a dick head.

I've done a lot of work with Bloodstock in the past and always applauded the safe, community-oriented atmosphere it champions.

So to see one of its organisers spout transphobic nonsense while issuing the famous 'I'm sorry if you were offended' apology is beyond disappointing.
